cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is about robot warehouse automation and specifically focuses on the Amazon Picking Challenge, which is a robotics competition. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques, such as segmentation and object recognition, which suggests that cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with 3D object pose estimation, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
